## App Scanning: When and How

### When Do We Scan?

| Trigger | Action |
|---------|--------|
| **First app launch** | Full scan, cache all apps |
| **App restart** | Quick check for new apps |
| **24+ hours since last scan** | Background refresh |
| **User requests** | Manual "Refresh" button (future) |

