### Why Cache the Results?

**Without caching:**
```
Session Start → Scan apps (3-5 seconds) → Show loading → Start session
```

**With caching:**
```
Session Start → Load from database (50ms) → Start session immediately
```

**User experience difference:** 3-5 seconds feels slow. 50ms feels instant.

